[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 4.8,
    "text": "Hello, and welcome to English for Everyone, where we practice real-life American English."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 4.8,
    "endTime": 9.0,
    "text": "Today, we're going to talk about some difficult pronunciations, so let's get started."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9.0,
    "endTime": 15.120000000000001,
    "text": "Recently, I got a request from one of our members to make a video about these difficult words and how to pronounce them correctly."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.12,
    "endTime": 17.04,
    "text": "So, this one's for you, Daniel."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.04,
    "endTime": 18.04,
    "text": "Keep watching."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.04,
    "endTime": 20.24,
    "text": "First, let's talk about this word."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.24,
    "endTime": 22.18,
    "text": "It's not pronounced I-oh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.18,
    "endTime": 23.74,
    "text": "We don't say I, I-oh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.74,
    "endTime": 27.279999999999998,
    "text": "We say oh, oh, I'll be right back."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.28,
    "endTime": 32.38,
    "text": "Not I'll be right back, but I'll, I'll, I'll be right back."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.38,
    "endTime": 33.38,
    "text": "Let's hear some examples."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.38,
    "endTime": 34.38,
    "text": "I'll be right back."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.38,
    "endTime": 35.38,
    "text": "Look, freeze."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.38,
    "endTime": 36.38,
    "text": "Don't move."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.38,
    "endTime": 37.38,
    "text": "I'll be right back."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.38,
    "endTime": 38.38,
    "text": "Okay?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.38,
    "endTime": 39.38,
    "text": "Don't move."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.38,
    "endTime": 40.38,
    "text": "I'll be right back."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.38,
    "endTime": 41.38,
    "text": "Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.38,
    "endTime": 42.38,
    "text": "Sorry, I gotta..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.38,
    "endTime": 43.38,
    "text": "I'll be right back."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.38,
    "endTime": 44.38,
    "text": "I'll be right back."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.38,
    "endTime": 45.38,
    "text": "All right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.38,
    "endTime": 46.54,
    "text": "We'll finish talking."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.54,
    "endTime": 47.66,
    "text": "Let's practice."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.66,
    "endTime": 51.66,
    "text": "Will you be right back?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.66,
    "endTime": 52.66,
    "text": "That's right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.66,
    "endTime": 53.66,
    "text": "I'll be right back."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.66,
    "endTime": 55.22,
    "text": "Now, let's look at this word."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.22,
    "endTime": 58.138999999999996,
    "text": "This word is pronounced it'll, it'll."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.139,
    "endTime": 62.56,
    "text": "The T changes to a fast D. Not it'll, but it'll, it'll."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.56,
    "endTime": 67.98,
    "text": "Then we go to the dark L. Oh, oh, oh, it'll."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.98,
    "endTime": 73.08,
    "text": "The last L sound is oh, like when you hear table or bottle."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.08,
    "endTime": 76.919,
    "text": "It's the same sound, oh, it'll, it'll."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.919,
    "endTime": 77.919,
    "text": "Example."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.919,
    "endTime": 79.419,
    "text": "We're having a party tomorrow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.419,
    "endTime": 80.61999999999999,
    "text": "You should come."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.62,
    "endTime": 81.62,
    "text": "It'll be fun."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.62,
    "endTime": 83.86,
    "text": "It'll, it'll be fun."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.86,
    "endTime": 84.9,
    "text": "Let's practice."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.58,
    "endTime": 86.58,
    "text": "We're having a party tomorrow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.58,
    "endTime": 90.94,
    "text": "Do you think it'll be fun?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.94,
    "endTime": 91.94,
    "text": "That's right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.94,
    "endTime": 92.94,
    "text": "It'll be fun."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.94,
    "endTime": 94.5,
    "text": "Now, let's talk about this contraction."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.5,
    "endTime": 95.5,
    "text": "You're."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.5,
    "endTime": 97.099,
    "text": "Yes, you can pronounce it like that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.099,
    "endTime": 100.98,
    "text": "You can say you're, making the ooh sound, you're."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.98,
    "endTime": 101.98,
    "text": "But normally we don't."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.98,
    "endTime": 103.94,
    "text": "We say you're, you're."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.94,
    "endTime": 109.419,
    "text": "So the pronunciation is just like the possessive you're, like your car or your phone."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.419,
    "endTime": 110.419,
    "text": "You're."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.419,
    "endTime": 111.419,
    "text": "Example."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.419,
    "endTime": 113.059,
    "text": "We're having a party tomorrow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.059,
    "endTime": 114.059,
    "text": "You're going to be there, right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.059,
    "endTime": 117.22,
    "text": "Yeah, I'm going to be there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.22,
    "endTime": 119.5,
    "text": "And what about this word, they're?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.5,
    "endTime": 123.22,
    "text": "You can pronounce the a, they, they're, but normally we don't."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.22,
    "endTime": 125.739,
    "text": "We say they're, they're."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.739,
    "endTime": 128.3,
    "text": "So these three words are pronounced exactly the same."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.3,
    "endTime": 136.53900000000002,
    "text": "They're, they are contraction, they're, like over there, and their, their car, their money."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.539,
    "endTime": 139.41899999999998,
    "text": "You can pronounce these words all exactly the same."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.419,
    "endTime": 141.339,
    "text": "So let's practice with they're."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.339,
    "endTime": 143.3,
    "text": "They're going to the store."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.3,
    "endTime": 147.94,
    "text": "They're, they're, they're going to the store."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.94,
    "endTime": 148.94,
    "text": "Let's practice."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.94,
    "endTime": 149.94,
    "text": "Where are they going?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.94,
    "endTime": 154.139,
    "text": "Are they going to the store?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.139,
    "endTime": 155.139,
    "text": "That's right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155.139,
    "endTime": 156.139,
    "text": "They're going to the store."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 156.139,
    "endTime": 159.86,
    "text": "And Daniel also asked about this word, world."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159.86,
    "endTime": 161.05900000000003,
    "text": "This is a hard one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.059,
    "endTime": 164.94,
    "text": "We use the er sound like burger, er, er, were."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.94,
    "endTime": 168.339,
    "text": "Then we go to the dark L. Listen."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168.339,
    "endTime": 176.86,
    "text": "World, world, world, world, world."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 176.86,
    "endTime": 179.5,
    "text": "It's like when you hear this word, girl."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 179.5,
    "endTime": 180.5,
    "text": "The same thing is happening."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.5,
    "endTime": 190.139,
    "text": "You're making the er sound like burger plus the dark L. Girl, girl, world, world."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 190.139,
    "endTime": 194.419,
    "text": "Example, I want to travel all over the world."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.419,
    "endTime": 195.419,
    "text": "What about you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 195.5,
    "endTime": 201.25900000000001,
    "text": "Do you want to travel all over the world?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 201.259,
    "endTime": 202.259,
    "text": "Very good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 202.259,
    "endTime": 205.13899999999998,
    "text": "So remember these difficult words to pronounce."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 205.139,
    "endTime": 211.25900000000001,
    "text": "I'll, it'll, your, their, and world."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 211.259,
    "endTime": 212.259,
    "text": "Thank you for watching."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 212.259,
    "endTime": 214.619,
    "text": "And if you like this video, subscribe to our channel."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 214.619,
    "endTime": 217.139,
    "text": "And if you want to become a member, click the Join button."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 217.139,
    "endTime": 217.899,
    "text": " And we'll see you next time."
  }
]